Show how university support for short-term placements
can promote positive learning processes in relation to
reection skills of student teachers.
(1) Evaluating a seminar designed to foster student
teachers‘ reection competences
(2) Assessing student teachers‘ reection com-
petence by using reection reports during their
practical assignment
(3) Exploring correlations between reection com-
petence and pedagogical beliefs
• Quasi-experimental study in a one-group pre-test-post-
test design
• Experimental group of student teachers (n=30)
• Control group of student teachers (n=30)
(a) pedagogical-psychological knowledge (BilWiss 2.0)
